<br>
Balanz, a proper damage to mana ratio is completely dependent on the amount of HP a mob has.  The more HP a mob has, the longer a fight is.  The longer a fight is, the more you need to make the most out of your mana.<br>
<br>
And about your italics and underlines, and whatever the heck else you use...it really is irritating.  Im sure when people type with caps lock on its pretty irritating to you.  Well it's the same thing with all your italics and whatnot.  Sorry I really dont mean to offend you, but I cringe when I read what you type.  It makes your arguments much tougher to follow because I am constantly asking myself &quot;Why does this text look different?  Why is it underlined? Why is it bold? Why is it italicized?&quot;  According to standard grammar, all the typing that you are adding to your text is very incorrect. <p><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" align="center">
